# Testing / coverage
# NOTE: leading slash on /coverage/ anchors the rule to repo root.
# Without it, ANY nested coverage/ folder is ignored — which silently
# excluded src/components/coverage/ from git for the whole Phase 2 +
# Phase 3.5 work and only surfaced when CI on Linux failed typecheck.
.coverage
/coverage/
htmlcov/
coverage.xml

